## Remarks  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/includes/deprecatedcontent-md.md)]  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="3aa8e-103">A <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.CompositeActivity> zarządza wykonaniem działania podrzędne przy użyciu <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionContext> klasy, metody i zdarzenia, zdefiniowany na <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity> klasy.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3aa8e-103">A <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.CompositeActivity> manages the execution of its child activities using <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionContext> class methods and events defined on the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity> class.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="3aa8e-104">Na przykład działanie podrzędne jest zaplanowana do wykonania przy użyciu <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionContext.ExecuteActivity%2A> z <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionContext>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3aa8e-104">For example, a child activity is scheduled for execution using the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionContext.ExecuteActivity%2A> of <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionContext>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3aa8e-105">A <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.CompositeActivity> może zostać poinformowany działania, po zakończeniu działania podrzędne działania jej wykonanie subskrybując <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity.Closed> zdarzeń zdefiniowane na <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3aa8e-105">A <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.CompositeActivity> activity can be notified when a child activity completes its execution by subscribing to the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity.Closed> event defined on <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="3aa8e-106">Środowisko wykonawcze przepływów pracy wymusza pewnych ograniczeń w <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.CompositeActivity> wykonania i najbardziej podstawowe, które jest fakt, że <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.CompositeActivity> działania nie można przenieść do <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity.Closed> stanie, jeśli wszystkie działania podrzędne są nadal w <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity.Executing>, <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity.Canceling>, <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity.Compensating>, lub <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity.Faulting>, stan.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3aa8e-106">The workflow runtime enforces certain constraints on <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.CompositeActivity> execution, the most fundamental of which is that a <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.CompositeActivity> activity cannot move to the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity.Closed> state if any child activities are still in a <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity.Executing>, <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity.Canceling>, <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity.Compensating>, or <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity.Faulting>, state.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="3aa8e-107">Ten przykład przedstawia podstawowe `CompositeActivity` , który jest wykonywany swoje pierwsze działanie podrzędne do wykonania.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3aa8e-107">This example shows a basic `CompositeActivity` that executes its first child activity for execution.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3aa8e-108">Jeśli działanie podrzędne jest przenoszony do stanu zwartego, działanie złożone jest powiadamiany o, a następnie kończy wykonywanie.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3aa8e-108">When the child activity moves to the Closed state, the composite activity is notified and then completes its execution.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
public class HasOneChildActivity : CompositeActivity  
{  
    protected override ActivityExecutionStatus Execute(ActivityExecutionContext executionContext)  
    {  
        Activity child = this.EnabledActivities[0];  
        child.Closed += this.ChildClosed;  
        executionContext.ExecuteActivity(child);  
  
        return ActivityExecutionStatus.Executing;  
    }  
  
    void ChildClosed(object sender, ActivityExecutionStatusChangedEventArgs e)  
    {  
        e.Activity.Closed -= this.ChildClosed;  
        ActivityExecutionContext executionContext = sender as ActivityExecutionContext;  
  
        executionContext.CloseActivity();  
    }  
}  
```
